            <%= @customer.curent_floor%>           
         </td>
      </tr>
      
      <tr>
         <td>
           <b>2.The total area of the object:</b>
         </td>         
         <td>
            <%= @customer.total_area%>sq.m.           
         </td>
      </tr>
       <tr>
         <td>
           <b>3.If not all of the developed area, specify the projected:</b>
